      "properties": {
        "url": [
          "https://irreverent.style/posts/not-invented-here/"
        ],
        "name": [
          "Not invented here"
        ],
        "published": [
          "2021-02-08"
        ],
        "category": [
          "technology",
          "innovation",
          "tools"
        ],
        "content": [
          {
            "html": "<p>On rolling your own tools/technology:</p>\n<figure class=\"c-blockquote\">\n<blockquote cite=\"https://craigmod.com/roden/050/\">\n<p>Use an off the shelf tool until you break it, until you hit its edges, then look for a solution. If that solution requires you to build something, then you have permission to build it, but only building out just enough to solve your creative issue.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figcaption class=\"c-blockquote__attribution\">— Craig Mod, <a href=\"https://craigmod.com/roden/050/\">Roden Issue 050</a></figcaption>\n</figure>",
            "value": "On rolling your own tools/technology:\n\n\nUse an off the shelf tool until you break it, until you hit its edges, then look for a solution. If that solution requires you to build something, then you have permission to build it, but only building out just enough to solve your creative issue.\n\n— Craig Mod, Roden Issue 050"
          }
        ]
      }
